	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can sometimes find Battlestaffs for sale in Erudin. 4pp from merchants. Useless as a weapon, but they give you +10 charisma. Only good for Paladins/clerics/warriors.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
