	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 22nd 4:09 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Personally I don't think spending 500pp on charisma items a good investment if you only plan on doing pottery.  Other skills maybe.  But to get from 0 to 100 in pottery only took me 11pp with a charisma of 75 and a wisdom of 80.  Granted it gets sligtly more expensive after that, but when you get to 148, you can sell your vials for a profit.  Just my 2 copper.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
